There are many guilds already out there... why one more? Because it's so hard to find a good &quot;fit&quot; sometimes with a guild, one that is just what you're looking for. That is the problem I and several others kept finding ourselves facing, and so we decided to create just what we have been looking for. Maybe it will be just what you have been looking for, too.<br>
<br>
We are Abiding Affinity. We are a good/neutral guild, with no restrictions on class, race, or season. We are a Family. Kindred spirits.<br>
<br>
There are many serious guilds, with lofty goals and weighty mission statements. We are simply a circle of friends who share the same vision, and hope to draw in others who seek the same things we do. There will always be evil in Norrath, and we will always fight it -- but we will have fun in between. We have no desire to be a huge guild, or a raiding guild, or a grind-grind-grind guild. We are not about warring, or constant dueling, or politics. We are simply a Family who wants to have fun together. Ale will usually be present. Pie fights are mandatory. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->         <br>
<br>
For once, have your guild list and your friend list be one and the same. We are Abiding Affinity... welcome home.<br>
<br>
<br>
Please feel free to join channel /affinity to speak with us and get to know us better, and visitors are always welcome in our <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub30.ezboard.com/beverkindred" target="top">Hall.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
